description: OFFER ACCEPTED! OPEN HOUSES CANCELLED...Quintessential Brick & Beam Loft in the renowned Court Square Press Building. This west facing unit with high ceilings & oversized windows, gets flooded with natural light & has beautiful skyline views at sunset. An open concept layout and acid wash concrete floors harmoniously blend with the original wood beams & exposed brick walls, evoking the building’s industrial heritage. The kitchen features leather granite countertops, a stainless-steel backsplash, & recently upgraded black stainless-steel Samsung appliances. A home office can easily be set up in the hallway, while the bedroom comfortably fits a king-sized bed & provides ample storage with 2 double closets. Superior amenities include 24/7 concierge, fitness facility, bike storage, screening/rec room, dog run, & outdoor terrace featuring a heated pool, BBQ grills, & herb garden. Conveniently located across from Broadway Station (Red Line) and all that Boston has to offer!
